---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | APIRank"
  description="APIRank is an independent AI API price comparison and review site, helping developers find the most cost-effective AI Token solutions."
>
  <div class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-600">Home</a>
        <span>›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">About</span>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About APIRank</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6 text-gray-700">
      <p>
        <strong>APIRank</strong> (apirank.vip) is an independent AI API price comparison and review site,
        dedicated to helping developers quickly find the most cost-effective AI Token solutions.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        The AI API market evolves rapidly — prices change monthly, new models emerge constantly, 
        and promotional activities come and go. As an independent site, we continuously track 
        provider updates and update pricing information in real time, so you don't have to 
        spend hours searching for information.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li>✅ <strong>Real-time Price Comparison</strong> — Coverage of 10+ major AI providers, input/output/cache pricing at a glance</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>In-depth Reviews</strong> — Real tests of model capability, response speed, API stability</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>China Accessibility Analysis</strong> — Which platforms are directly accessible from China, which require proxy</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Tutorials</strong> — Practical guides from registration to API calls</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Selection Recommendations</strong> — Best AI solutions for different use cases</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Monetization</h2>
      <p>
        We sustain operations through <strong>Google AdSense</strong> and <strong>Affiliate referral links</strong>.
        Some links are paid placements — we earn a commission when you click and make a purchase, 
        but this does not affect our objective review standards.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>For partnerships, corrections, or suggestions, feel free to contact us:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li>📧 Email: contact@apirank.vip</li>
        <li>💬 GitHub Issues: <a href="https://github.com/apirank/apirank.vip" class="text-blue-600 underline">Submit Issue</a></li>
      </ul>

      <div id="contact" class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          © 2025-{new Date().getFullYear()} APIRank<br/>
          Price data is for reference only. Actual prices may vary. Please check the official provider website for the most accurate information.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-3">
          Find me on About.me: <a href="https://about.me/jasonxmai" rel="me noopener" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline">jasonxmai</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
